<div class="inner" id="msg_1120335"><span style="font-size: 13pt;" class="bbc_size"><em>这色彩鲜艳的羽蛇周身散发着平和与睿智的气息 </em></span><br><hr /><span style="font-size: 14pt;" class="bbc_size"><span style="color: brown;" class="bbc_color"><strong> 太阳勇士领主 Lord Sun-Warrior，CR 15</strong></span></span><br><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>XP 51200</strong></span><br>独特羽蛇<br>秩序善良 大型异界生物（本地）<br><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>先攻</strong></span> +7；<span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>感官</strong></span> 黑暗视觉60呎，侦测秩序/混乱/善良/邪恶；<span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>察觉</strong></span> +32<br><hr /><span style="font-size: 12pt;" class="bbc_size"><span style="color: green;" class="bbc_color"><strong>防御</strong></span></span><br><hr /><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>AC</strong></span> 28，碰触 13，措手不及 24 （+3敏捷，+1闪避，+15天生，-1体型）<br><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>HP</strong></span> 230（20d10+120）<br><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>强韧</strong></span> +14，<span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>反射</strong></span> +17，<span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>意志</strong></span> +19<br><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>免疫：</strong></span>影响心灵的效果<br><br><hr /><span style="font-size: 12pt;" class="bbc_size"><span style="color: green;" class="bbc_color"><strong>攻击</strong></span></span><br><hr /><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>速度</strong></span> 20尺，飞行60尺（机动性普通）<br><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>近战</strong></span> 噬咬+26 （2d6+10 附加摄抓与毒素）<br><strong><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color">占据</span></strong> 10尺 <strong><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color">触及</span></strong> 10尺<br><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>类法术能力</strong></span>（施法者等级9 专注+15）<br>恒定—侦测混乱，侦测邪恶，侦测善良，侦测秩序<br>随意使用—变身术，侦测思想 (DC 18)，幻化灵体（施法者等级18），隐形术, 异界传送（DC18）<br>1次/每年—许愿术<br><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>特殊攻击</strong></span> 紧勒（2d6+10）<br><hr /><span style="font-size: 12pt;" class="bbc_size"><span style="color: green;" class="bbc_color"><strong>数据</strong></span></span><br><hr /><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>已知术士法术 （施法者等级12 专注+18）</strong></span><br>6环—（4/日）连环闪电（DC 22）<br>5环—（6/日）生命之息，焰击术（DC 21）<br>4环—（7/日）魅惑怪物（DC 20），行动自如，次等指示术<br>3环—（7/日）气化形体，人类定身术，反邪恶法阵，召唤怪物III<br>2环—（8/日）治疗中伤，鹰之威仪，闪光尘（DC 18），灼热射线，沉默术（DC 18） <br>1环—（8/日）忍受环境，法师护甲，隐雾术，防护混乱，克敌机先<br>0环（随意）—舞光术，晕眩术，侦测魔法，打击死灵，光亮术，冰冻光线，阅读魔法，提升抗力，稳定伤势<br><br><br><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>力量</strong></span> 24，<span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>敏捷</strong></span> 17，<span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>体质</strong></span> 22，<span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>智力</strong></span> 19，<span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>感知</strong></span> 20，<span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>魅力</strong></span> 23<br><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>BAB</strong></span> +20；<span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>CMB</strong></span> +28（+32擒抱）；<span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>CMD</strong></span> 42（无法被绊摔）<br><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>专长</strong></span> 警觉（Alertness），顽强（Diehard），闪避（Dodge），法术强效（Empower Spell）施法免材（Eschew Materials），飞越攻击（Flyby Attack）,强韧加强（Great Fortitude）， 精通先攻(Improved Initiative), 精通天生武器：噬咬（Improved Natural Attack：BIte）钢铁意志（Iron Will），闪电反射（Lightning Reflexes）<br><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>技能</strong></span> 特技+26（跳跃时+22），唬骗+19，交涉+29，飞行+24，知识（奥秘）+14，知识（位面）+17，知识（宗教）+17，察觉+32，察言观色+ 32，法术辨识+27，生存+25，使用魔法装置+26 <br><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>语言</strong></span> 天界语，通用语，龙语，精灵语，混通语（Polyglot）；心灵感应100尺<br><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>特殊能力</strong></span> 毒素<br><hr /><span style="font-size: 12pt;" class="bbc_size"><span style="color: green;" class="bbc_color"><strong>特殊能力</strong></span></span><br><hr /><br><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>毒素（EX）：</strong></span>噬咬伤害; 强韧检定 DC 22; 频率 每分钟一次，持续10分钟; 效果 1d4 力量伤害; 连续通过两次检定则治愈。此毒素DC基于体质。<br><br><strong><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color">法术：</span></strong>太阳勇士可以如12级术士一样施展法术，它也可以施展来自牧师法术列表的法术就如这些在术士的法术列表内一样。对于太阳勇士而言牧师法术被视为奥术，这意味着它不需要法器来施展法术。 <br><br>作为莽吉荒原中Utala部落的古老守护者而闻名，Mola Jushujaa（其名字的意思是“太阳勇士”）曾以许多不同的面貌出现在许多不同的地方。它是一只年长的羽蛇，在羽蛇中广受尊重。由于其崇高的地位，Jushujaa 拥有许多普通羽蛇所没有的能力，包括改变自身的外表、以及在战斗中呼唤可畏的火焰与闪电风暴的能力，甚至拥有实现愿望的力量（尽管这一能力只为实现最大的善而服务）。它经常化身为温和亲切的老人或青年去拜访那些强大的统治者、祭司和贵族，为他们提供指引或劝阻他们走上邪恶之路。<br><br>太阳勇士领主独立于任何神祇行事，尽管它与所有善良阵营的存在都保持着积极的关系。它拥有相当复杂的计划，涉及到在许多不同的世界促进和平的文化与国家的发展，以及救赎或彻底毁灭邪恶的存在。因而，它经常招募冒险者和其他特工，并派遣他们去执行那些或许不会马上展现出影响的任务，并尽可能为他们提供指引和帮助。它得到了它的捍卫者 Jua Mfuasi（秩序善良 男性人类 艾奥梅黛的圣武士10）的帮助，他过去曾经是一个被称为尸骸王（Corpse King）的死灵法师，直到他被太阳勇士杀死并复活，之后他放弃了他的邪恶之道和奥术魔法，转而成为了一名圣武士。 <br><br><br><div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px"><div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px"><b>剧透</b> - &nbsp;<i> </i>: <input type="button" value="顯示" style="width:60px;font-size:10px;margin:0px;padding:0px;" onClick="if (this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display != '') { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = ''; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;this.innerText = ''; this.value = '隐藏'; } else { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = 'none'; this.innerText = ''; this.value = '显示'; }"></div><div class="alt2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px; border: 1px inset;"><div style="display: none;">Couatl, Lord Sun-Warrior<br>This brilliantly colored couatl radiates a palpable air of peace and wisdom.<br>Lord Sun-Warrior CR 15<br>Source Mythical Monsters Revisited pg. 14<br>XP 51,200<br>Unique couatl<br>LG Large outsider (native)<br>Init +7; Senses darkvision 60 ft., detect chaos/evil/good/law; Perception +32<br>Defense<br>AC 28, touch 13, flat-footed 24 (+3 Dex, +1 dodge, +15 natural, –1 size)<br>hp 230 (20d10+120)<br>Fort +14, Ref +17, Will +19<br>Immune mind-affecting effects<br>Offense<br>Speed 20 ft., fly 60 ft. (average)<br>Melee bite +26 (2d6+10 plus grab and poison)<br>Space 10 ft., Reach 10 ft.<br>Special Attacks constrict (2d6+10)<br>Spell-Like Abilities (CL 9th; concentration +15)<br>Constant—detect chaos, detect evil, detect good, detect law<br>At will—alter self, detect thoughts (DC 18), ethereal jaunt (CL 18th), invisibility, plane shift (DC 23)<br>1/year—wish (CL 20th)<br>Sorcerer Spells Known (caster level 12th; concentration +18)<br>6th (4/day)—chain lightning (DC 22)<br>5th (6/day)—breath of life, flame strike (DC 21)<br>4th (7/day)—charm monster (DC 20), freedom of movement, lesser geas<br>3rd (7/day)—gaseous form, hold person, magic circle against evil, summon monster III<br>2nd (8/day)—cure moderate wounds, eagle’s splendor, glitterdust (DC 18), scorching ray, silence (DC 18)<br>1st (8/day)—endure elements, mage armor, obscuring mist, protection from chaos, true strike<br>0 (at will)—dancing lights, daze, detect magic, disrupt undead, light, ray of frost, read magic, resistance, stabilize<br>Statistics<br>Str 24, Dex 17, Con 22, Int 19, Wis 20, Cha 23<br>Base Atk +20; CMB +28 (+32 grapple); CMD 42 (can’t be tripped)<br>Feats Alertness, Diehard, Dodge, Empower Spell, Eschew MaterialsB, Flyby Attack, Great Fortitude, Improved Initiative, Improved Natural Attack (bite), Iron Will, Lightning Reflexes<br>Skills Acrobatics +26 (+22 when jumping), Bluff +19, Diplomacy +29, Fly +24, Knowledge (arcana) +14, Knowledge (planes) +17, Knowledge (religion) +17, Perception +32, Sense Motive +32, Spellcraft +27, Survival +25, Use Magic Device +26<br>Languages Celestial, Common, Draconic, Elven, Polyglot; telepathy 100 ft.<br>Special Abilities<br>Poison (Ex) Injury—bite; save Fortitude DC 22; frequency 1/minute for 10 minutes; effect 1d4 Str; cure 2 consecutive saves. The DC is Constitution-based.<br><br>Spells Sun-Warrior casts spells as a 12th-level sorcerer, and can cast spells from the cleric list as well as from those normally available to a sorcerer. Cleric spells are considered arcane spells for couatls, meaning Sun-Warrior does not need a divine focus to cast them.<br>Description<br>Best known as the ancient guardian of the Utala tribe in the Mwangi Expanse, Mola Jushujaa (whose name means “Lord Sun-Warrior”) has appeared in many different lands and guises. He is a couatl of great age, and his pronouncements are well respected among the feathered serpents. Because of his venerable status, Jushujaa has a number of powers that lesser couatls do not possess, including the ability to change his appearance, create terrifying fire and lighting storms in combat, and even grant wishes (though only ever in service to the greatest possible good). He often takes the guise of an extremely old or young human, inoffensive and peaceful, visiting powerful rulers, priests, and nobles to either offer guidance or dissuade them from the path of evil.<br><br>Lord Sun-Warrior acts independently of any deity, though he maintains positive relations with all of the good-aligned ones. His agenda is complex, but involves fostering the development of peaceful cultures and nations throughout many different worlds, and the discouragement or outright destruction of evil ones. In this he frequently recruits adventurers and other agents, dispatching them on quests that may not immediately make sense, and providing them with guidance and assistance as he is able. He is aided in his efforts by his champion, Jua Mfuasi (LG male human paladin of Iomedae 10), who was once a necromancer known as the Corpse-King until he was killed and returned to life by Sun-Warrior, after which he renounced his evil ways and abandoned arcane magic to become a paladin.</div></div></div></div>
</div>
